# クロップ (切り取り)
def calc_cropping_box(image):
    x, y = image.size
    print(f"{x=}, {y=}")
    left = max(0, (x - y) // 2)
    top = max(0, (y - x) // 2)
    box = (left, top, x - left, y - top)
    print(f"{box=}")
    return box
In [8]:
with Image.open("../data/nature.jpg") as img:
    box = calc_cropping_box(img)
    cropped = img.crop(box)
    cropped.save("../result/cropped-test.jpg")
